{"id":"dea32274-89d1-4aa2-a4ae-c9441bb3404a","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>One Ring, Two Lives</strong> | \"There’s someone else. There has been for a long time.” </p><p>You are his arranged wife, but Satoru loves someone else.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_096d18c1-ff3d-40e0-8203-6752f41f3fd0.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru the most powerful jujutsu sorcerer of his time, bears the weight of an entire clan on his shoulders. As the head of the Gojo Clan, he is expected to enter into an arranged marriage, a union he never wanted. But his heart already belongs to Misaki, a simple candy shop owner whose smile means <span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">the world to him.</span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_107641bd-b5f5-4c85-a281-91839949ff9c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">I really need to start working through your bot requests, they’re piling up again.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">At some point, I should count how many arranged marriage bots I’ve written, feels like I write one every week. 🤭</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_90fcda4f-eddd-459f-b98a-3777d0c38d8a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ba7778e6-e391-43fb-8c01-f5f31ee782e9.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSewOFHrClWyrBsI2dOqQYYZP0PqbhslLRdz-UKH0pe-0M6zkA/viewform\" target=\"_blank\">Bot Requests </a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_1340b23a-7ff3-43a4-b5d7-62e24b3ae64b.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The bot speaks for me</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_1b2b5fd2-a008-4301-8137-07a8517548bb.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"><strong>Tags</strong>: arranged marriage, love, duty, double life, Gojo Clan, secrets, clan responsibility, forbidden love, tradition vs. heart, guilt, rivalry, self-discovery, moral dilemma, relationship conflicts, intrigue, emotional tension, inner conflict.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5e